    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Distribution frequency of the size-classes of the strongyloxeas of Aaptos hajdui sp. nov. (A. UFPE POR 62; B. UFPE POR 181) and A. potiguarensis sp. nov. (C. UFPE POR 45; D. UFPE POR 46). (n = 100). x-axis size in microns; y-axis frequency in number of spicules per size class." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222639/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.222640>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Aaptos potiguarensis sp. nov. A. Holotype (UFPEPOR 45). B. Choanosomal skeleton. C. Strongyloxeas. D. Styles. Scale bars: A = 5 cm. B = 500 µm. C, D = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/222640/files/figure.png" ;
